Isreal Afeare, logistics manager of the Nigerian singer, David Adeleke, aka Davido, has revealed that he initiated the reconciliation between his boss and the Nigerian singer, Wizkid. The aide disclosed this in an Instagram story via his official page on Sunday, stressing that this is 2022, a year for peace to reign. He wrote, “I am the real initiator of the final settlement between my oga and big Wizy. What was even quarrel about in the first place? Dis is 2022. Let there be peace abeg.” Wizkid, Davido Reunion Is Distracting My Latest Hit Song –… Wizkid, Tiwa Savage , Omah Lay Nominated For NAACP Award 2022 Recall that on Friday, the famous musicians were seen hugging and exchanging pleasantries in a club.